Package gr.aueb.dmst.onepercent.programming

Class DataBase

java.lang.Object
gr.aueb.dmst.onepercent.programming.DataBase
public class DataBase extends Object
Class: DataBase is responsible for interacting with the H2 database. It provides methods for creating tables, inserting data, and querying information.

    • createDatabase

      public void createDatabase()
      Method: createDatabase() creates tables in the H2 database. Creation of 4 tables: 1) Metrics (ID, Date) 2) Container(ID,C_ID, C_NAME, Status, Image_ID, Network_ID, Gateway, IP_Address, Mac_Address) 3) Image (ID,NAME) 4) Measure (ID,C_ID, Cpu_usage)
